description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Roll dice with up to 16 people in a rush to 10,000 points! With single, local and online play, the more people you beat the higher your ranking goes! Share your ranking with the people you play and show the world your skill!
